      "content": "thanks. i checked the logs and everything looks fine on the digital side, so it's not a software glitch. we also checked the security footage and haven't seen any obvious theft or anything like that. it's just these weird little gaps popping up randomly. do you think there are other more technical or logistical reasons for these tiny losses?",
